comments: Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) brushes Edwards? (MIN) off-arm, causing marginal contact to occur on the driving shot attempt.
Replay review of the out-of-bounds called on Gobert (MIN) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed successful. Dort (OKC) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Gobert (MIN) engages and disengages with Williams (OKC) off-ball and marginal contact occurs as Williams (OKC) moves to defend the shot.
Russell (MIN) moves alongside Dort?s (OKC) path and marginal body contact occurs with a collapsed forearm during the driving shot attempt.

Omoruyi (OKC) swipes up and makes marginal contact with Edward (MIN), which does not affect his ability to secure the rebound.
Dort (OKC) and Towns (MIN) mutually engage during the rebound, and the contact is marginal.

Before the free throw, Russell (MIN) delays time before getting to the line.
Towns (MIN) contests the driving shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Gilgeous-Alexander?s (OKC) arm after the release.

Russell (MIN) delivers contact to Dort (OKC) that dislodges Dort (OKC) from his legally obtained defensive position.
Dort (OKC) commits a take foul on Edwards (MIN).
